9:17 AM Defendant Davonte R Underwood in court, in custody.  Prosecuting attorney Randy P. Sitzberger in court for the State of Wisconsin. Attorney Luis Daniel Gutierrez in court for Davonte R Underwood. Attorney appears as friend of the court. 

Attorney Gutierrez states he would have been appointed on this case but due to this case being sealed, they are unable to e-file in this case and would have to file the order appointing counsel in person.  Defendant has informed Attorney Gutierrez that he is planning to retain private counsel for his preliminary hearing.  The defendant states he is uncertain of his attorneys name but spoke with his mother and the attorney on the telephone but are having difficulties having his counsel visit him in the jail.  The Court finds good cause to adjourn the preliminary hearing and will set an additional status of counsel date.  Court tolled time limits for preliminary hearing.  State did have a witness present for the preliminary hearing that was set for today.  Bail remains as fixed.
